title: Five Fingers
description: Game Warden Charley Cove is struggling to stop a bloody string of deer shot and left in the snow. He’s stymied by a lazy prosecutor and a dirty deputy–plus the tug of two cultures running through his veins. Cove uncover’s evidence that ties the shooter to crimes against people, and unknown to the warden, his bad guy is about to come unglued and drag his bloodbath into a horrific nightmare for a two legged victim.
author: Tony H. Latham
